Surprise Given Mahlangu resides at Paardeplaas, where his home is situated on the other side of the highway across from the school. He was fatally injured when he crossed the N4 around 06:25 on July 13. Paramedics were called to the scene where he was declared deceased. On the same day, Machadodorp police confirmed, an older male was also killed on the N4 when he was fatally struck between town and the Machadodorp Toll Plaza. The unidentified male was riding a bicycle on his way home from work. No further details were provided.